title: Greenhouse Effect Coffee
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe specializing in crepes both savory and sweet. Savory crepes include sometimes (but not always) a vegan crepe - call ahead to check if the vegan crepe batter is in stock or not. Sweet crepes can be made with strawberries, bananas, and house-made chocolate syrup. Drinks include chai, coffee drinks, tea, and Italian sodas. Free Wi-Fi.
